web.feedback.help_us_improve.text: Āwhinatia mātou ki te whakapai ake

web.feedback.help_content_goes_here.text: Ka noho te ihirangi āwhina ki konei.

web.feedback.thanks_for_helping_onetime_.text: Ngā mihi mō tō āwhina ki a Onetime Secret ki te whakapai ake. He mea nui tēnei.

web.feedback.weve_built_this_tool_to_hel.text: Kua hangaia e mātou tēnei taputapu hei āwhina i a koe ki te tuari mōhiohio tairongo i runga i te haumaru, ā, he mea nui ō wheako ao-tūturu mō te arotahi i ā mātou mahi. Ka āwhina i a mātou ki te whakatau he aha te mahi ā muri ake nei me te pēhea te whakapai ake i te ratonga mō te katoa.

web.feedback.hey_there_thanks_for_stoppi.text: Tēnā koe, ngā mihi mō tō toro mai ki tā mātou whārangi urupare. Ehara tō kōrero i te mea pōwhiri noa - he mea nui.

web.feedback.a_note_from_delano_founder_.text: He tuhipoka mai i a Delano, kaiwhakarewa o Onetime Secret
